snippet.title: Miniclip: Egg Run Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is another old Miniclip flash game, where you navigate the egg through high and low platforms to catch a wooden twig before passing a level. The way I see it, the flash game's stages remind me of Sonic the Hedgehog because of the sand color and green on top in every single level. What do you guys think?
